        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Initializes the test suite and creates test cases.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-arrays Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_ARRAYS calls. Fixed function pipeline.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-arrays-vsh Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_ARRAYS calls. Custom vertex shader.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlinebuffers Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_BUFFERS calls. Fixed function pipeline.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlinebuffers-vsh Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_BUFFERS calls. Custom vertex shader.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlinearrays Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_ARRAYS calls. Fixed function pipeline.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlinearrays-vsh Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_ARRAYS calls. Custom vertex shader.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlineelements Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_ELEMENTS calls. Fixed function pipeline.</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="remark"><para>TinyDraw-inlineelements-vsh Renders hundreds of tiny triangles using individual DRAW_INLINE_ELEMENTS calls. Custom vertex shader. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
